{
  "stem": "54.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They brought us over to the-- to the bungalows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where each bungalow took in about 1,000 people-- they were only woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we slept on those bunkers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was under-- lucky, I was on the lower bunker. 10 girls slept with me on the lower bunker.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Each of us, we were laying on the side, like the-- we were like the herring, to each, next to each other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the top was the same thing. 1,000 people they put in, in this bungalow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we couldn't even pull out our head from under the bungalow-- I mean the bunker, to catch a little bit of air, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the Germans used to come in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If somebody had his hair-- sticked out his head, out of the bunker, so you got, with a stick, they gave us a over the head with a stick.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So everybody was inside, was quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were afraid to open up our mouths.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And 5 o'clock in the morning, they called us outside-- winter, when snow was outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to punish us, we had to kneel in the snow from 5 o'clock in the morning until 8 o'clock in the morning, until they made appell for us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they were-- they were counting us, if nobody run away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to have the right figures, you know, of the people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can imagine that nobody from us could stand up anymore, because our-- we didn't have any feet anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No knees, no feet, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came into the-- into the bungalow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They give us something to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The food was only a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all day long, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
